OL,3,CTyson Fury: I moved my family to the
OL,4,CIsle of Man to escape 'nut jobs'
OL,6,FBoxer Tyson Fury has revealed he was
OL,7,Fforced to move to the Isle of Man to
OL,8,Fescape the "nut jobs" that left him
OL,9,Ffearing for the safety of his family.
OL,11,FFury moved his wife Paris and their
OL,12,Fseven children from Morecambe in 2025
OL,13,Fbecause of the number of disturbed
OL,14,Fvisitors who would arrive at his house
OL,15,Fat all hours of the day and night.
OL,17,FThe 'Gypsy King' who takes on
OL,18,FArslanbek Makhmudov in his latest
OL,19,Fcomeback fight at Tottenham Hotspur
OL,20,FStadium on Saturday, says the Isle of
OL,21,FMan already feels like home.
OL,26,@pD@LOUpD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
