OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776082266
OL,3,CTyson Fury: I moved my family to the
OL,4,CIsle of Man to escape 'nut jobs'
OL,6,F'He's a scary dude': When and where
OL,7,Fcan you watch Fury vs Makhmudov?
OL,9,F"When people know where you live, you
OL,10,Fcan be targeted at any time, so now I
OL,11,Fhave moved and my address is
OL,12,Fconfidential," Fury said.
OL,14,F"The final straw was when I had a
OL,15,Flunatic come over my gates ` 40feet
OL,16,Fgates. I've got an attack dog, I've
OL,17,Fgot everything. The police came and he
OL,18,Fsaid: 'I'm here to be adopted by Tyson
OL,19,Fand Paris'.
OL,26,@qD@AOUtD@NO]vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
