CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776082266
OL,3,CTyson Fury: I moved my family to the
OL,4,CIsle of Man to escape 'nut jobs'
OL,6,F"I wasn't home, I was at the gym and
OL,7,FParis phoned me going nuts. This man
OL,8,Fcould have had a knife or anything on
OL,9,Fhim.
OL,11,F"I also had to disconnect my intercom
OL,12,Fon the gates because it was going all
OL,13,Fnight, every weekend.
OL,15,F"I had crackpots, drunk people,
OL,16,Fparking outside the front of the house
OL,17,Fringing the bell asking 'is Tyson in'?
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
