CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776082266
OL,3,CTyson Fury: I moved my family to the
OL,4,CIsle of Man to escape 'nut jobs'
OL,6,F"I've had a million nut jobs at my
OL,7,Fplace. One time there was a guy and he
OL,8,Fwas dressed in seashells from head-to-
OL,9,Ftoe, looked like an absolute lunatic.
OL,10,FHe said 'God sent me here to speak to
OL,11,Fyou'.
OL,13,F"But my manager Spencer Brown offered
OL,14,Fhim 20 quid and he grabbed it and
OL,15,Fvanished. These people are innocent
OL,16,Fbut when is it going to be one who
OL,17,Fisn't innocent?
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
