PN,39805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776082266
OL,3,CTyson Fury: I moved my family to the
OL,4,CIsle of Man to escape 'nut jobs'
OL,6,F"I was actually targeted by foreign
OL,7,Frobbers too, they came to the UK to
OL,8,Frob me and some other famous people
OL,9,Fand then run back to their country.
OL,11,F"I'm not down about it, I lived in
OL,12,FMorecambe for 20 years, so it was time
OL,13,Ffor a change.
OL,15,FTyson Fury claims to be most famous
OL,16,Fattraction in Morecambe ahead of
OL,17,FNetflix show launch
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU
