OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1776082266
OL,3,CTyson Fury: I moved my family to the
OL,4,CIsle of Man to escape 'nut jobs'
OL,6,F"I looked at moving abroad, far away,
OL,7,Fbut it turned out that the Isle of Man
OL,8,Fis the perfect place for me ` English
OL,9,Fspeaking, English pound notes.
OL,11,F"I can go and get an English newspaper
OL,12,Ffrom the local petrol station with my
OL,13,Fcoffee and speak my own lingo."
OL,15,FFury has come out of retirement for
OL,16,Fthe fifth time after 16 months of
OL,17,Finactivity in what will be his first
OL,18,Fhome appearance since defeating Derek
OL,19,FChisora in 2022.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUuD@_O]
