OL,3,CTyson Fury: I moved my family to the
OL,4,CIsle of Man to escape 'nut jobs'
OL,6,FA win over Makhmudov would bring an
OL,7,Fall-British showdown with Anthony
OL,8,FJoshua a step closer.
OL,10,FHe said: "I dreamed as a child of
OL,11,Fbeing the heavyweight world champion
OL,12,Fand I have lived it. It's absolutely
OL,13,Ffabulous to be back in boxing. The
OL,14,Fcircus continues."
OL,26,@rD@JOUvD@RO]
